title: Unemployment rate in Jamaica 2019
summary: In general Unemployment rate has rose over the Year.
Unemployment rate is slightly increasing from 2007 to 2010.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 12.37 was reported at Year 2010
Minimum Unemployment rate about 9.75 was reached at Year 2007
